text: "Sweetest Pie" is a pop rap song by American rapper Megan Thee Stallion and British singer Dua Lipa, released on March 11, 2022. It is from Stallion's second studio album Traumazine, as it is the lead single in that album. Comercially, the song has peaked through the top 10 in Canada, Hungary, The Netherlands, and The United States. ==References== Category:2022 songs Category:Rap songs Category:Dua Lipa songs Category:Megan Thee Stallion songs
